During the prior three elections 96% or more of House incumbents who
ran for re- election won.  Most Americans believe that career
politicians are more concerned with their self-preservation that with
people's concerns.  A solution to this problem is term limits.  Many
political scientists do not agree that term limits are good.</SUM>
